FNF: Crossed Out · Free Game · Play Online

Rating: 4.4 · Your rating: n/a · Total votes: 1163

FNF: Crossed Out is a must-play Friday Night Funkin' song based on FNF: Indie Cross. Cuphead, Sans and Bendy are back to challenge Boyfriend to a 5-minute-long music rhythm battle. Do you accept the challenge?

August 04, 2022 // Added the Undertale mini-games and the [Super Potato Sprites] option

Made by Unbekannt0 (Coder, Charter) and Mike Geno (Composer).
